      "title": "Three Plateaus of Adult Mental Development",
      "text": "In the Contructive Development Theory, Kegan presents a 5 state model of intellectual capacity. The first 2 stages relate to pre-adolescence, the last 3 relate to adult development. Very few reach the 5th stage, that of a \"self-transforming mind\"."
    },
